name: Poopy Pigeon 030
description:
We live by the code: RGBP red green blue poop.

Poopy Pigeons x jmh_wwyg
Poopy JMY Pigeon is a special collab with @jmh_wwyg (also see @marble.tez), it is the first collaborative pigeon and the first interactive pigeon.

Poopy Pigeons are 1/1 pixel pigeons that poop. There are 500 pigeons to be collected!
